    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184310/extras/07d608d82bf31af209073f72e4ff86cd.poster.avif?t=1769025932\" width=600 height=246 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184310/extras/07d608d82bf31af209073f72e4ff86cd.webm?t=1769025932\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184310/extras/07d608d82bf31af209073f72e4ff86cd.mp4?t=1769025932\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > You are the sole survivor of a devastating spaceship crash, stranded on a frozen, desolate planet. Now, you must scavenge whatever scraps remain in a desperate attempt to call for help.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Remote-Controlled Exploration</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184310/extras/260ffd59291ddf5aabfacb24c41a7e9e.poster.avif?t=1769025932\" width=600 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184310/extras/260ffd59291ddf5aabfacb24c41a7e9e.webm?t=1769025932\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184310/extras/260ffd59291ddf5aabfacb24c41a7e9e.mp4?t=1769025932\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Trapped within the hollow shell of your ship, deploy a scrap recovery bot to venture into the outside world. Search for what scarce resources this planet offers and uncover the mystery behind your crash.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >An Unfolding Landscape</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184310/extras/660e5f4fba459f20104aac1452d61d1a.poster.avif?t=1769025932\" width=598 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184310/extras/660e5f4fba459f20104aac1452d61d1a.webm?t=1769025932\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184310/extras/660e5f4fba459f20104aac1452d61d1a.mp4?t=1769025932\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Severe weather conditions constantly reshape the world around you, revealing new areas along with what lies dormant beneath.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A Mystery</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184310/extras/045ed44c5a9328edef4d4a79a7d6ce62.avif?t=1769025932\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184310/extras_big/045ed44c5a9328edef4d4a79a7d6ce62.avif?t=1769025932 width=800 height=228 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >On this planet full of secrets, it's up to you to piece together the puzzle. Use your journal to document your findings and uncover the truth before it’s too late.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A Slow Descent into Madness</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184310/extras/24090456c386769a66cfa3f466aeb2d3.poster.avif?t=1769025932\" width=600 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184310/extras/24090456c386769a66cfa3f466aeb2d3.webm?t=1769025932\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184310/extras/24090456c386769a66cfa3f466aeb2d3.mp4?t=1769025932\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The cold makes sleep elusive, blurring the line between reality and paranoia. Whatever lurks in the shadows, you don't want to linger long enough to confront it.</p>",
